Expat Life Insurance & Income Protection | HealthCare International



















































Call us +44 (0)207 590 8800
Contact us











Pay online Apply










Life insurance
At HealthCare International, we have more than 35 years experience in the international insurance sector, so we have real expertise in delivering insurance solutions that meet the needs of internationally mobile workers and expatriates.
When you move from country to country, your life risks change considerably. So for anyone with dependents or commitments, putting life insurance in place makes real sense.
For many expats and globally mobile workers, too many life insurers complicate costly policies with exclusions. At HealthCare International, we do things differently.
 
Get a quote
FAQs




Benefits
The benefits of our international life insurance include:

a choice of life cover options and premiums appropriate for your particular circumstances
our insurance policies are fully flexible to reflect your new circumstances - for example, new-borns or a house purchase
24-hour claims line, 365 days a year, for immediate emergency assistance and advice

To complement our international life insurance products, we also offer a critical illness plan that will provide you with a lump sum cash payment if you are diagnosed with a critical illness. And for extra security, we offer income protection to cover your ongoing financial obligations should you suffer an accident or injury serious enough to keep you away from work for an extended period of time.
Alongside our individual life insurance policies, we offer corporate group life and income protection insurance programmes for life and income protection insurance – and if our standard insurance plans don’t quite fit company health care requirements, we can create a tailored solution.
We make our life insurance claims and settlements procedure as simple, straightforward and sympathetic as possible, so that families are spared any unnecessary worry about their financial future.
Alongside our international life insurance, critical illness and income protection plans, we also offer other products tailored to the needs of expats and internationally mobile workers, including medical cover and travel insurance.
For more information please call +44 (0)20 7590 8800 or download a HealthCare International Life Insurance Brochure here.






