Worldwide Travel Insurance | HealthCare International



















































Call us +44 (0)207 590 8800
Contact us











Pay online Apply










Worldwide Travel Insurance
We all hope to avoid accidents and emergencies, particularly when we are travelling away from home. But if they do happen when you’re on holiday or working abroad, HealthCare International offers international travel insurance cover to meet the needs of world travellers, expatriate families, employees and employers.
Whether you’re affected by lost luggage or missing airline tickets, a delayed or cancelled flight or a medical emergency, all you need to do is call our 24/7/365 emergency helpline for expert advice and support to resolve your problem.
We also offer insurance plans that provide a broader range of travel cover, including for personal accident, lost passports, travel delay, missed departures, legal expenses and hijack.
Annual Multi-Trip Travel policies cover certain winter sports at no extra cost and for up to 17 days per policy year. This can be added to our Single Trip Travel Plan as an optional extra.
 
Get a quote
FAQs




Benefits
We offer the following Travel Insurance benefits:

an annual multi-trip travel plan for the most frequent global travellers, which will cover as many trips abroad, to any destination, that you wish to make each year, up to a maximum of 90 days per trip
a single trip travel plan, to cover trips abroad of up to 90 days.

On our Annual Multi-Trip Travel Plan, we offer five levels of travel cover, so that you can choose the one that’s right for you.
All travel insurance plans cover cancellation of flights and curtailment of travel arrangements, medical expenses, and accidental loss, damage or theft or your possessions and also cover for your lost baggage, personal possessions, money and documents, such as lost passport or tickets.
We offer our international travel insurance plans on an individual or family basis (children under 18 must be accompanied by an insured adult or subject to a special arrangement - please contact us) and can tailor corporate travel plans to the needs of larger businesses or organisation. We also offer travel plans to clients under our affinity schemes, for smaller businesses, partnerships, clubs, associations and other groups with a shared interest.
For more information please call +44 (0)20 7590 8800 or download an international travel insurance brochure here.






