International Medical insurance
Whether you are looking for an all-inclusive international health insurance policy or a simpler product that covers just the medical emergency basics, HealthCare International has a health care plan that’s right for every expat.
At HealthCare International, our focus is on putting our clients’ medical needs first. So no matter what your personal circumstances may be or where in the world you are living or working, our international medical insurance plans are designed to deliver the health care solution you are looking for.
The built-in flexibility of our health insurance products also means that our plans are able to keep pace with you and your family through life, as your medical needs change.
 
View our plans
Get a quote
FAQs
Testimonials




Benefits
The benefits of our international health insurance include:

access to more than 7,000 worldwide medical centres and 350,000 physicians and nursing staff in more than 160 countries
our own 24-hour, 365-day medical emergency assistance service and access to global healthcare network of 24/7 medical professionals and centres
we can arrange emergency transport to the nearest appropriate medical centre, or repatriation

Membership is open to virtually everyone, provided they join before the age of 75, and we are committed to keeping any restrictions linked to past or pre-existing medical conditions to an absolute minimum. We also welcome applications for health cover from people aged 75 onwards, when will just need to ask a few additional medical questions.
For employers, we offer corporate healthcare group programmes as a valuable employee medical benefit and if our standard plans don’t quite fit company health care requirements, we can create a tailored insurance solution.
To complement our international medical insurance plans for expats, we also offer a range of other insurance protection products, including life insurance, income protection and critical illness cover and worldwide travel insurance.
For more information please call +44 (0)20 7590 8800.






